OL,7,FThe chief fire officer (CFO) and
OL,8,Fassistant chief fire officer (ACFO) of
OL,9,FShropshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,10,Fboth sent messages suggesting they
OL,11,Fwanted to kill or harm female
OL,12,Fcolleagues.
OL,14,FIn the WhatsApp messages - which have
OL,15,Fbeen leaked to ITV News - the senior
OL,16,Fofficers also use the words "lazy
OL,17,Fcow", "bint" and "useless" to refer to
OL,18,Fwomen in the service.
