OL,7,FSeveral of the messages target Area
OL,8,FManager Jan Morris, who resigned from
OL,9,Fthe service this year after reading
OL,10,Fwhat had been said about her.
OL,12,F"She does the square root of f***
OL,13,Fall," the now ACFO Adam Matthews
OL,14,Fmessaged in February last year.
OL,16,F"I've got no loyalty to the lazy cow,"
OL,17,Fhe added in March 2023.
OL,19,FHe then shared a cartoon GIF of
OL,20,Fsomeone being thrown under a bus.
