OL,7,FHis boss, Simon Hardiman, who is now
OL,8,FCFO, wrote about Jan in March 2022,
OL,9,Fsaying: "At least she had a positive
OL,10,Feffect on the gender pay gap," before
OL,11,Fadding several laughing emojis.
OL,13,FHe talked about sending a job advert
OL,14,Ffrom another service to Jan, before
OL,15,Fasking "does that look too forceful?".
OL,17,FSeveral months later in June 2022, the
OL,18,FCFO stated simply: "I've calmed down
OL,19,Fnow but I could still kill her buddy."
